definitions.definition: A seal which can magically transform into a human by shedding its skin.
A common , harbor seal ( Phoca vitulina ), or grey seal ( Halichoerus grypus ).

main_definition: ( Celtic mythology ) A seal which can magically transform into a human by shedding its skin.
secondary_definitions: ( Scotland , Shetland ) A common , harbor seal ( Phoca vitulina ), or grey seal ( Halichoerus grypus ).
